<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الِانْشِقَاق<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{إِذَا السَّمَاءُ انْشَقَّتْ , وَأَذِنَتْ لِرَبِّهَا وَحُقَّتْ , وَإِذَا الْأَرْضُ مُدَّتْ , وَأَلْقَتْ مَا فِيهَا وَتَخَلَّتْ}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٤ص١٠٦:</span> <span class="c3">{وَأَذِنَتْ}</span>: سَمِعَتْ وَأَطَاعَتْ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c3">{وَأَلْقَتْ}</span>: أَخْرَجَتْ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{مَا فِيهَا}</span>: مِنَ المَوْتَى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c3">{وَتَخَلَّتْ}</span>: عَنْهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الانشقاق: ١ - ٤]</p> </div>